{
  "stem": "26111.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A very brief space of time-- I mean, my parents must have been absolutely horrified.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, how come?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How come?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm sure she told them the whole story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They must have told Ada because that's the only way that she could have known.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My rational thinking told me that, that they were dead, that they had-- they were not in good health.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all the things that one learned-- and I was, remember, I was in intelligence-- US intelligence at the end of the war, just after the war.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had access to certain-- to certain information.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of that later became general information.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all that went learned about the divisions that the Nazis made among the people that were deported shows that the, the only people that really had a chance were those that were young able-bodied, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was, at that time, in '43, he would be 58 years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had never been an athletic-type person. 58 in 1943 in Germany is not like 58 [LAUGHS] in, in, in, in the US today.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother, of course, was ailing on a fairly long-term basis-- this, this asthma and other related things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she was not well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- there's, there's no reason, rational reason to, to believe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing is that there is-- that hope springs eternal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But hope gets extinguished as the mortality-- even if they did live and escape-- it gets extinguished as one gets older and as one's parents would be older.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so there came a time when I had to simply say--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I tried, tried, tried, tried-- I, I kept trying to find out more from all-- god, there's a myriad of organizations, lists.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One can always find out more information.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
